room_title: Escape room "The Lost Prophecy" by Let Us Go Escape Rooms in Muskegon

room_description:
You’ve finally found the home of the archaeologist we’ve been searching for.

He’s believed to have all 4 of the missing pieces to the ancient artifact that can predict the end of mankind.

Quick, retrieve the pieces and escape before time runs out!
